]) \}
$ECENTER
$PAR

(b) Using the matrix obtained in your answer for part (a) as the initial matrix, next perform the row operations 
$PAR
\(\qquad \qquad -$a21 R_1 +R_2 \to R_2\)
$PAR
\(\qquad \qquad -$a31 R_1 + R_3 \to R_3.\)
$PAR
